&lt;p&gt;Although the landscape of travel has changed, your well-being remains our highest priority. &amp;nbsp;As you consider your future travel plans to San Francisco, we assure you that we are monitoring the COVID-19 situation every day and taking proactive steps to ensure the health and safety of our guests and staff.&amp;nbsp; On behalf of everyone at Hotel Nikko San Francisco,&amp;nbsp; stay safe, and thank you for your continued loyalty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A2-Feature Snippet&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;read-more-target&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;overview-boxspacer&quot;&gt;Feature Box 1: AAA Best of Housekeeping Hotel&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;overview-boxspacer&quot;&gt;In our 30 year history, we&#039;ve been known for our rigorous cleaning procedures, being named a AAA &amp;lsquo;Best of Housekeeping&#039; property for 2020. We continue to deep clean with hospital-grade disinfectants along with expanded COVID-19 protocols. You can expect to see enhanced procedures in every area of the hotel.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feature Box 2: Highest Standards of Cleaning&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are committed to upholding the highest quality of standards and have enhanced our cleaning and disinfecting procedures. Partnering with industry-leading experts, CHLA &amp; the CDC, Ecolab and Clorox, we&#039;re enhancing cleanliness and using new protocols to provide you with the ultimate in hospitality and service in the same manner you have become accustomed to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hand sanitizer and disinfecting wipes available in guest rooms and at high-touch points throughout the hotel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Increased frequency of cleaning public spaces, including the front desk, the concierge desk, elevators and elevator buttons, door handles, public bathrooms, and room keys.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional deep cleaning of high-touch surfaces and best practices for pools, fitness centers, and lounges.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;occsnip-name&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feature Box 3: For Your Protection&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;column21&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All guests and employees are required to wear masks in public spaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proof of Vaccination is required for entry into the Health Club and Gym, Swimming Pool, Feinstein&#039;s at the Nikko, Restaurant ANZU and Kanpai Lounge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hotelier training and certification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
